text: Anthony Beckett (born 1884, date of death unknown) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:Year of death missing Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
